name: Patty Gurlo
description: So what can I say about me, well I’m pretty down to earth not afraid to roll up my sleeves and get dirty if i have to, independent, hard working, intelligent,, pretty easy to talk to and i’ve been told I’ve got a good sense of humor. I love to travel, visiting new places is so exciting to me. Being immersed in different cultures is truly an awesome experience. I like to dance ,I enjoy going out to dinner or going to see a movie. I’m also open to outdoor activities like going fishing or adventurous stuff, its nice to mix it up from time to time. However I’m also perfectly fine kicking back on the couch and staying in for the night.
